Class DockableBarEvent

java.lang.Object
  java.util.EventObject
      java.awt.AWTEvent
          com.jidesoft.action.event.DockableBarEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class DockableBarEvent
extends java.awt.AWTEvent

An AWTEvent that adds support for DockableBar objects as the event source.

See Also:
DockableBar, DockableBarListener, Serialized Form
